OL,3,CThree people arrested for murder after
OL,4,Cman found injured and dog stabbed
OL,6,FThree people have been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder after a man died
OL,8,Fin Burtwood this morning (5th May).
OL,10,FStaffordshire Police were called to
OL,11,FHazel Grove before 9 o'clock in the
OL,12,Fmorning after reports of two men
OL,13,Ffighting.
OL,15,FWest Midlands Ambulance paramedics and
OL,16,Fpolice officers found a man with
OL,17,Fserious injuries. He was pronounced
OL,18,Fdead at the scene.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
