OL,3,CThree people arrested for murder after
OL,4,Cman found injured and dog stabbed
OL,6,FA dog was found with what police
OL,7,Fsuspect to be stab wounds, and is
OL,8,Fbeing treated by a vet.
OL,10,FTwo men aged 32 and 27 and a woman
OL,11,Faged 33 have been arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,14,FOfficers have put a cordon in place at
OL,15,Fthe home and set up a public portal
OL,16,Ffor people to report any information.
